{"words":[{"word":"book","count":5},{"word":"remember","count":4},{"word":"yes","count":3},{"word":"ash","count":3},{"word":"place","count":3},{"word":"echo","count":2},{"word":"time","count":2},{"word":"old","count":2},{"word":"vault","count":2},{"word":"made","count":2},{"word":"memory","count":2},{"word":"i've","count":2},{"word":"young","count":1},{"word":"lady","count":1},{"word":"seems","count":1},{"word":"fond","count":1},{"word":"reading","count":1},{"word":"actually","count":1},{"word":"communicating","count":1},{"word":"speak","count":1},{"word":"responds","count":1},{"word":"questions","count":1},{"word":"ask","count":1},{"word":"spend","count":1},{"word":"understand","count":1},{"word":"carried","count":1},{"word":"everywhere","count":1},{"word":"heard","count":1},{"word":"helped","count":1},{"word":"design","count":1},{"word":"coded","count":1},{"word":"lock","count":1},{"word":"letter","count":1},{"word":"saw","count":1},{"word":"indeed","count":1},{"word":"page","count":1},{"word":"tearing","count":1},{"word":"fit","count":1},{"word":"clean","count":1},{"word":"bathroom","count":1},{"word":"punishment","count":1},{"word":"hehe","count":1},{"word":"course","count":1},{"word":"hazy","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"dangerous","count":1},{"word":"sorry","count":1},{"word":"fine","count":1},{"word":"child","count":1},{"word":"feels","count":1},{"word":"familiar","count":1},{"word":"lived","count":1},{"word":"long","count":1},{"word":"hmm","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"others","count":1},{"word":"faces","count":1},{"word":"blur","count":1},{"word":"rarely","count":1},{"word":"left","count":1},{"word":"taking","count":1},{"word":"train","count":1},{"word":"somewhere","count":1},{"word":"dark","count":1},{"word":"mistaken","count":1},{"word":"group","count":1},{"word":"scholars","count":1},{"word":"home","count":1},{"word":"try","count":1},{"word":"expert","count":1},{"word":"sort","count":1},{"word":"thing","count":1},{"word":"date","count":1},{"word":"innocent","count":1},{"word":"truthseeker","count":1},{"word":"wrongfully","count":1},{"word":"convicted","count":1},{"word":"fools","count":1},{"word":"memories","count":1},{"word":"hurt","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"hesitated","count":1},{"word":"sacrifice","count":1},{"word":"truth","count":1},{"word":"carry","count":1},{"word":"burden","count":1},{"word":"perhaps","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"stay","count":1},{"word":"focused","count":1},{"word":"lies","count":1},{"word":"ahead","count":1},{"word":"work","count":1},{"word":"name","count":1},{"word":"lily","count":1},{"word":"section","count":1},{"word":"oversee","count":1},{"word":"card","count":1},{"word":"alright","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"used","count":1},{"word":"wanted","count":1},{"word":"sleep","count":1},{"word":"among","count":1},{"word":"echoes","count":1},{"word":"study","count":1},{"word":"behaviors","count":1},{"word":"stubborn","count":1},{"word":"man","count":1},{"word":"ash's","count":1},{"word":"id","count":1},{"word":"stolen","count":1},{"word":"outsiders","count":1},{"word":"done","count":1},{"word":"least","count":1},{"word":"twenty","count":1},{"word":"years","count":1},{"word":"fuzzy","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"It's an Echo book, young lady, and it seems fond of you. You think you're reading it, but it's actually the book communicating with you.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"Yes. It doesn't speak, but it responds to the questions you ask. The more time you spend with it, the more you'll understand it.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"Old Ash carried this book everywhere. I heard it even helped him design a coded lock for the vault.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"That letter you saw is indeed a page from this book. I remember Ash tearing it out in a fit once. We all made him clean the bathroom as a punishment, hehe.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"Of course.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"My memory is hazy... I do remember something dangerous out there, but that's all. I'm sorry.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"...","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"I'm fine, child. This place feels so familiar. It's like I've lived here for a long time.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"Hmm... this place. I've been here before with many others, but their faces are a blur...","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"Yes, we rarely left this place, but I do remember taking the train somewhere very dark...","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"Yes, if I'm not mistaken, a group of scholars made a home for themselves here.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"You might want to try the Echo book. It's an expert at this sort of thing.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"The date when an innocent truthseeker was wrongfully convicted by fools. I remember, but the memories hurt.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"They never hesitated to sacrifice for the truth. They shouldn't have had to carry such a burden.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"Perhaps, but for now we must stay focused on what lies ahead.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"All I know is that I do work in the vault, and my name is... Lily.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"But this isn't the section I oversee. Why am I here... Why are you here?","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"I only have this card.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"...","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"Alright, I'll come with you.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"Old Ash? He used to say he wanted to sleep among the Echoes to study their behaviors. What a stubborn man.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009},{"text":"Ash's ID was stolen? Outsiders couldn't have done that—we've been in here for at least twenty years. Even with my fuzzy memory, I know that much.","quest_name":"Silent as a Falling Leaf","quest_id":122000009}]}